item.title: Let's contribute to OSS with Go
item.description: I’ll talk about what I noticed when I contributed to Go OSS for the first time, and ‘Why’ and ‘Why Not’ contribute to OSS (in English). The target audience is as follows - 1-2 year Go experience. Who has no contribution to OSS. Who want to contribute to OSS.
